[media]

**Full Game:** 

**meta.com/experiences/6743334779111805**

 **discord.gg/pdvr (pixel dungeon vr)** join to win gifts!

With **core gameplay of Dungeons of Eternity & Ancient Dungeon**, upgrade **Battle Talent's combat thrills**, this co-op game brings you into **VR Minecraft** world to explore the unknown！
[media]

# 💥Boss Fight, Awesome Every Time
**Skull King** swings his axe, little skulls run to attack you. **Ghost Lord** blows things up & shoots bullets to chase you! **Angel** turns into giant eye monster & fires lasers everywhere. **God of Time** smashes the ground & throws everyone into 2nd battleground - battles get more exciting!
[media]

# ⚔️Rich Weapons, Always Something New
Throw **Captain America's shield** to hit enemies! Use **Wolverine's claws** to tear up monsters! Become **Hawkeye, shoot with longbow**!

**Find a treasure box? Hurry!** Open it for rare weapons! 

**Level up your gear!** 2 stars to 3 stars? Damage doubles!
[media]

# 👑Tons of Hero Looks, Customize Yours!
**The Witcher, Black Knight, Bird Man**...so many heroes to choose from. 

**Unlock skin rewards** - who says you can't look cool in dungeons?
[media]


# ✨Free Version - Still Fun!
- **Random maps** every time! **Explore freely like Minecraft**.
- **Play with friends!** Fight monsters together - super exciting! Rock-paper-scissors in the dungeon? - have tons of laughs!
- **Rich scenes**: Forbidden library, creepy prison, old ruins...
- **Talent tree**: Fast dodges or huge damage attacks, learn new skills every time!
- **Monster chaos**: Cute slimes bounce, scary skeletons laugh, and spiders crawl— crush their nests fast!

[media]
